documentation.text: @title This contract provides an interface for the flow buffers
@notice Returns true if conditions for minting are satisfied.
@notice Triggers a minting step, if the enough number of blocks had elapsed.
@notice Returns the % of remaining tokens that the contract will output on each "mintStep" call in stage I

@notice The constant amount of  tokens that the contract will output on each "mintStep" call
 in stage II until target is reached.
@notice How many tokens will be minted for this address
@notice Returns the remaining amount to mint.
@notice Returns the cut-off value where the constant emission stage II starts
@notice Returns the minimum number of blocks between minting steps
@notice Returns the block number from where the mint step can be issued
@dev Return the current in-bound token balance
@dev Return the current out-bound token balance
@dev Returns `true` if there is enough inbound tokens to trigger exchange orders *
@dev Returns `true` if there is enough outbound tokens to trigger exit *
@dev Triggers an exit order transferring the exit threshold amount to the output account *
